    {
      "id": "csa-s125",
      "number": "125",
      "text": "125 The definitions in this section apply in this Part. aid to navigation means a buoy, beacon, lighthouse, landmark, radio aid to marine navigation or any other structure or device installed, built or maintained in or on water or on land for the purpose of assisting with marine navigation. Minister means the Minister of Fisheries and Oceans. VTS Zone means a Vessel Traffic Services Zone established under paragraph 136(1)(a).",
